owl:Ontology.dc:title: VEKG - Vocabulário para descrição de Enterprise Knowledge Graphs
owl:Ontology.rdfs:comment: VEKG: Vocabulário para Descrição e Representação de Enterprise Knowledge Graphs - Conceituado a partir de Termos e Conceitos que constituem a definição de um EKG.

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A top concept or entry point for a void:Dataset that is structured in a tree-like fashion. All resources in a dataset can be reached by following links from its root resources in a small number of steps.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: root resource

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Defines a simple URI look-up protocol for accessing a dataset.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has an URI look-up endpoint at

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Defines a regular expression pattern matching URIs in the dataset.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has URI regular expression pattern

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A vocabulary that is used in the dataset.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: vocabulary

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: The rdfs:Class that is the rdf:type of all entities in a class-based partition.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: class

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A subset of a void:Dataset that contains only the entities of a certain rdfs:Class.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: class partition

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An RDF dump, partial or complete, of a void:Dataset.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Data Dump

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Points to the void:Dataset that a document is a part of.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: in dataset

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: The dataset describing the objects of the triples contained in the Linkset.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Objects Target

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: An OpenSearch description document for a free-text search service over a void:Dataset.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: open search description

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: The rdf:Property that is the predicate of all triples in a property-based partition.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: property

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: A subset of a void:Dataset that contains only the triples of a certain rdf:Property.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: property partition

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: The dataset describing the subjects of triples contained in the Linkset.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Subjects Target

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: One of the two datasets linked by the Linkset.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Target

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The graphs associated with the subject and object are equivalent.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: equivalent graph

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The graph associated with the subject is a subgraph of a graph equivalent to that associated with the object.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: subgraph of

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The total number of distinct classes in a void:Dataset. In other words, the number of distinct resources occuring as objects of rdf:type triples in the dataset.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: classes

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The total number of distinct objects in a void:Dataset. In other words, the number of distinct resources that occur in the object position of triples in the dataset. Literals are included in this count.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: distinct objects

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The total number of distinct subjects in a void:Dataset. In other words, the number of distinct resources that occur in the subject position of triples in the dataset.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: distinct subjects

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The total number of documents, for datasets that are published as a set of individual documents, such as RDF/XML documents or RDFa-annotated web pages. Non-RDF documents, such as web pages in HTML or images, are usually not included in this count. This property is intended for datasets where the total number of triples or entities is hard to determine. void:triples or void:entities should be preferred where practical.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: number of documents

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The total number of entities that are described in a void:Dataset.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: number of entities

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The total number of distinct properties in a void:Dataset. In other words, the number of distinct resources that occur in the predicate position of triples in the dataset.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: number of properties

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The total number of triples contained in a void:Dataset.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: number of triples

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: A URI that is a common string prefix of all the entity URIs in a void:Dataset.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: URI space

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A set of RDF triples that are published, maintained or aggregated by a single provider.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Dataset

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A collection of RDF links between two void:Datasets.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Linkset

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The term “data asset” is synonymous with “data source”
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Data asset

owl:Class.dc:title: Global Semantic View of Graph
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Global Semantic View
Visão Semântica Global

owl:Class.vocab:definition: Uma LinkRule é uma propriedade (rdf:Property) que é utilizada para descoberta de uma ligação (Link) entre dois recursos (rdfs:Resource) - source e target.
owl:Class.drm:destination: Um Objeto rdfs:Resource (Target) relacionado por uma LinkRule.
owl:Class.drm:origin: Um Sujeito rdfs:Resource (Source) relacionado por uma LinkRule.
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Uma LinkRule é uma propriedade (rdf:Property) que é utilizada para descoberta de uma ligação (Link) entre dois recursos (rdfs:Resource) - source e target.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Link Rule
Regra de Link

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Uma Visão de Linkset é uma representação de uma Ligação (Link) entre Linksets e LinkRules.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Linkset View

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Uma Ontologia Local é por definição um vocabulário formal e explícito contendo os termos e conceitos que descrevem uma fonte de dados específica.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Local Ontology
Ontologia Local

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Propriedade utilizada para comparação com base em uma Link Rule (Regra de Ligação).
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Metric
Métrica

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A Linked Data Platform Resource (LDPR) whose state is represented as RDF.
owl:Class.rdfs:label: RDFSource

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A CSV document broadly conforming to IETF's RFC4180 (http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4180); csv:hasEscapeSymbol and csv:hasColumnDelimiter are both set for this class (\ and , respectively)
owl:Class.rdfs:label: CSV Document
Documento CSV

owl:NamedIndividual.VEKG:rmlVision: SELECT SUBSTRING(cnpj,0,9) as root_cnpj,cnpj , REPLACE(regexp_replace(nome_fantasia, '[^a-zA-Z ]', '', 'g'),' ','_') as nome_uri, REPLACE(regexp_replace(razao_social, '[^a-zA-Z ]', '', 'g'),' ','_') as razao_uri,razao_social, CASE WHEN opc_simples = '' OR opc_simples = '0' THEN 'NAO_OPTANTE' WHEN opc_simples = '5' OR opc_simples = '7' THEN 'OPTANTE' WHEN opc_simples = '6' OR opc_simples = '8' THEN 'EXCLUIDO' END as opc_simples, CASE opc_mei WHEN 'S' THEN 'true' WHEN 'N' THEN 'false' ELSE NULL END as opc_mei, q.id_uri as id_qualif, n.id_uri as id_nat FROM public.empresas INNER JOIN qualificacao_socio q ON qualif_resp::int = q."CÓDIGO" INNER JOIN natureza_juridica n ON cod_nat_juridica::int = n.id WHERE empresas.matriz_filial = '1' AND SUBSTRING(cnpj,0,9) = '03995515'

SELECT org.RJU_RUC_JURIDICO, org.RJU_RAZON_SOCIAL, org.RJU_SIGLAS, org.RJU_FEC_INCORPORACION, RJU_FEC_ACTUALIZACION, org.RJU_TAB_COD_UNIDAD, org.RJU_TUS_COD_USUARIO, RJU_TIP_SOCIEDAD, org.RJU_DATA_ULT_ALT, CONCAT('0',SUBSTR(RGE_CGC_CPF,0,8)) CNPJ FROM TULIOSEMANTIC.RUC_JURIDICOS org, TULIOSEMANTIC.RUC_GENERAL geral WHERE org.RJU_RUC_JURIDICO = geral.RGE_RUC AND geral.RGE_TIP_PERSONA = 2 AND (org.RJU_RUC_JURIDICO, CONCAT('0',SUBSTR(RGE_CGC_CPF,0,8))) = ANY ( SELECT MIN(RGE_RUC),CONCAT('0',SUBSTR(RGE_CGC_CPF,0,8)) FROM TULIOSEMANTIC.RUC_GENERAL GROUP BY(CONCAT('0',SUBSTR(RGE_CGC_CPF,0,8))) HAVING (COUNT(*) > 1) )

owl:NamedIndividual.VEKG:transformationFunction: if(S) then true when (N) then false

SELECT org.RJU_RUC_JURIDICO, org.RJU_RAZON_SOCIAL, org.RJU_SIGLAS, org.RJU_FEC_INCORPORACION, RJU_FEC_ACTUALIZACION, org.RJU_TAB_COD_UNIDAD, org.RJU_TUS_COD_USUARIO, RJU_TIP_SOCIEDAD, org.RJU_DATA_ULT_ALT, CONCAT('0',SUBSTR(RGE_CGC_CPF,0,8)) CNPJ FROM TULIOSEMANTIC.RUC_JURIDICOS org, TULIOSEMANTIC.RUC_GENERAL geral WHERE org.RJU_RUC_JURIDICO = geral.RGE_RUC AND geral.RGE_TIP_PERSONA = 2 AND (org.RJU_RUC_JURIDICO, CONCAT('0',SUBSTR(RGE_CGC_CPF,0,8))) = ANY ( SELECT MIN(RGE_RUC),CONCAT('0',SUBSTR(RGE_CGC_CPF,0,8)) FROM TULIOSEMANTIC.RUC_GENERAL GROUP BY(CONCAT('0',SUBSTR(RGE_CGC_CPF,0,8))) HAVING (COUNT(*) > 1) )
